OL,3,CBirmingham's striking bin workers
OL,4,Coffered voluntary redundancy
OL,6,FBirmingham's striking bin lorry
OL,7,Fdrivers are being offered voluntary
OL,8,Fredundancy in a fresh attempt by the
OL,9,FCity Council to resolve the all-out
OL,10,Fdispute.
OL,12,FBirmingham City Council said a "large
OL,13,Fnumber of expressions of interest" had
OL,14,Fbeen received from bin workers, and
OL,15,Foffers of financial packages were
OL,16,Fcurrently being issued.
