OL,3,CBirmingham's striking bin workers
OL,4,Coffered voluntary redundancy
OL,6,FIt said this was part of "service
OL,7,Fredesigns across the council." More
OL,8,Fthan two hundred drivers work at the
OL,9,Fthree city depots in Kings Norton,
OL,10,FTyseley and Perry Barr.
OL,12,FUnite the Union said that the offer of
OL,13,Fredundancies "is not a resolution -
OL,14,Fand if there is a genuine redundancy
OL,15,Fsituation, it would always make sense
OL,16,Fto release the agency workers first."
OL,18,FIt comes as bin workers said they
OL,19,Fwould "strike for the rest of the year
OL,20,For as long as it takes to get a fair
OL,21,Fdeal."
