OL,3,CBirmingham's striking bin workers
OL,4,Coffered voluntary redundancy
OL,6,FThe bin strike, which started in
OL,7,FJanuary over pay and the removal of
OL,8,Froles, was before all-out industrial
OL,9,Faction began on March 11.
OL,11,F"They are rushing it through"
OL,13,FDespite talks to resolve the
OL,14,Fsituation, no deal has yet been struck.
OL,16,FUnite has since claimed that
OL,17,FGovernment commissioners are
OL,18,F"blocking" a deal from being made to
OL,19,Fend the dispute.
