OL,3,CBirmingham's striking bin workers
OL,4,Coffered voluntary redundancy
OL,6,FOne grade-four city driver said
OL,7,F"Emails have been going out (within
OL,8,Fthe last week) with figures.
OL,10,F"They (the council) are trying to
OL,11,Fbreak the strike that way by offering
OL,12,Fthe VR.
OL,14,F"They are rushing it through. I just
OL,15,Fthink they are trying to reduce the
OL,16,Fnumbers on the picket lines.
OL,18,F"Some of these workers are long term.
OL,19,FSome might take it (if they are near
OL,20,Fretirement), but it all depends on
OL,21,Findividual circumstances."
