OL,4,Coffered voluntary redundancy
OL,6,FA City Council spokesperson said
OL,7,F"Voluntary redundancy options have
OL,8,Fbeen offered to workers as part of
OL,9,Fservice redesigns across the council
OL,10,Fthroughout the last year.
OL,12,F"A large number of expressions of
OL,13,Finterest in voluntary redundancy have
OL,14,Fbeen received from within the waste
OL,15,Fservice, and we are following our
OL,16,Fusual processes in progressing those
OL,17,Fexpressions of interest to offers over
OL,18,Fthe coming weeks."
OL,20,F"The offer of redundancies is not a
OL,21,Fresolution"
